r>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10762.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Warrior damage question</span><hr size=1> What do most warriors go for?<br>
2hs for max damage a little slower or,<br>
2-1hs for faster damage? <br>
<br>
got a 21 War coming up and just wondering what most do. Now he has been using Mithril 2hander, crits in the 90's.<br>
 Looking for opinions.<br>
<br>
